         <div type="commentary" subtype="frontmatter" xml:space="preserve">
          <p>This papyrus has been digitally edited by Elisabetta Alletto and Susanna Bertone and revised by Vincenzo Damiani as part of the Project <ref target="http://www.kallimachos.de/kallimachos/index.php/Anagnosis:Main">Anagnosis</ref> and the <ref target="http://epikur-wuerzburg.de/aktivitaeten/thv/">Würzburger Zentrum für Epikureismusforschung</ref></p>
          </div>
         <div xml:lang="grc" type="edition" xml:space="preserve">
<div n="1" subtype="column" type="textpart" corresp="#FR8861"><ab>
<lb n="1"/>ἐπιτηδείοις γίνεσθαι
<lb n="2"/>ἐθιστέον δρόμῳ καὶ τά
<lb n="3" break="no"/>χει καὶ ὅτι οὐ ψιλοὺς δεῖ
<lb n="4"/>τρέχειν ἀλλὰ μεθ’ ὅπλων.
<milestone rend="paragraphos" unit="undefined"/>
<lb n="5"/>ἐφίππους δὲ λέγει δρό
<lb n="6" break="no"/>μους τοὺς διαύλους τρέ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>χοντας τέσσαρας. τά
<lb n="8"/>δὲ βαρέα ἀντὶ πάλης ἐν
<lb n="9"/>ὅπλοις <unclear>π</unclear>οιε<unclear>ῖ</unclear> ἕνα πρὸς
<lb n="10"/>ἕνα καὶ δύο πρὸς δύο
<lb n="11"/>ἕως δέκα καὶ δέκα. καὶ
<milestone rend="paragraphos" unit="undefined"/>
<lb n="12"/>γυναιξὶ δέ φησι μεταδο 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>τέο<unclear>ν</unclear> κ<unclear>όρ</unclear>αις, εἶτα ὅτ<unclear>ι</unclear> <unclear>καὶ</unclear>
<lb n="14"/>ἵπποις ἀγωνιστέον. με 
<milestone rend="paragraphos" unit="undefined"/>
<lb n="15" break="no"/>τὰ ταῦτα πρὸς σωφρο
<lb n="16" break="no"/>σύνην ἀσκῆσαι βουλό
<lb n="17" break="no"/>μενος περὶ τῆς συνου
<lb n="18" break="no"/>σ<unclear>ίας</unclear> <unclear>β</unclear>ούλεται παραινεῖν 
<lb n="19"/>ὅπως μὴ ἥττους ὦσι, καὶ
<lb n="20"/>περὶ ἔρωτος ὅτι τριττός
<lb n="21"/><unclear>ἐσ</unclear>τιν ὁ μὲν ψυχῆς καὶ
<lb n="22"/><unclear>το</unclear>ῦ κα<unclear>λ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ο</supplied><unclear>ῦ</unclear> κ<unclear>ατα</unclear><gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="character"/>
<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/> </ab>
</div>  
